Say '''Bobon''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Northern Samar]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 20,956 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 130 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6401.	
															
